Please read the doc https://geos-chem.readthedocs.io/en/stable/getting-started/quick-start.html firstly!!!
This doc contains only about how to run the geoschem on IAP's Earthlab.

Step1:
Download the geoschem classic or GCHP from git.
git clone --recurse-submodules https://github.com/geoschem/GCClassic.git /path/in/your/cluster/GCClassic
git clone --recurse-submodules https://github.com/geoschem/GCHP.git /path/in/your/cluster/GCHP

Use command below to change the Version to you prefer.
git checkout tags/Version you like

Step2:
Create Run dir.
bash ~/GCClassic/run/CreateRunDir.sh
Then choose the relative setting for your simulation
